-- Third Point hedge fund has big EBay stake, talked with CEO-source
-- By Svea Herbst-Bayliss
-- Tue Sep 30, 2014 11:38AM EDT
-- None



BOSTON, Sept 30 (Reuters) - Hedge fund manager Daniel Loeb's Third Point LLC has taken a "significant" stake in online marketplace EBay Inc <EBAY.O> and had discussions with its chief executive officer, a source familiar with the matter said on Tuesday.

